<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error | JioHotstar</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #030b17;
            --surface-color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
            --accent-color: #0078ff;
            --error-red: #ff4444;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            /* Subtle radial gradient for depth */
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #0f172a 0%, #030b17 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 3rem;
            background: var(--surface-color);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: inline-block;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.3));
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 120, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 120, 255, 0.5);
            background: #0084ff;
        }

        /* Glitch effect for the 404 / Error text (Optional) */
        .error-code {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 15rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            z-index: -1;
            user-select: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="error-code">ERROR</div>

    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">ðŸŽ¬</div>
        <h2>Oops! Link Broken</h2>
        <p>Hume maaf kijiye, par ye content abhi hamare universe mein available nahi hai. Shayad ye kisi dusre planet
            par chala gaya!</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Wapas Home Par Chalo</a>
    </div>

</body>

</html>